data.description: Our most popular split plan is BACK! Hurry! This ones a beauty and backs to greenbelt acreage! Gorgeous spacious  family home with gorgeous custom cabinets, all granite tops, beautiful spacious  kitchen & full pantry. Covered back porch with sunset views.
data.whatILove: Excellent commute to Metro Tulsa just minutes to loving your country mile! Gorgeous open views & extra large lots make our popular split plan just one of the many good reason to check out our builds in Pioneer Estates! Open split plan where builder upgrades are our standard construction features! ALL custom knotty alder cabinetry throughout! All granite counter tops for every surface. Beautifully designed tile splash & master spa baths make for upgrades you'll appreciate! Loads of kitchen cabinetry, full pantry storage, mud room & home office center, oversized laundry room. Spacious master suite & bath. Oversized living room & two guest rooms with large closets & shared full bath. Extra space to roam with nearly 3/4 acre lot! Garden & play outdoors! Come see us we're almost SOLD OUT!
